  "text": "Coping strategies are the ways an individual, group or organization use to minimize the effects of stress [CITATION_1] ). Coping strategy is defined as \"any activity, in thought or deed, which has as its goal the removal or modification of a threat to identity\" (Breakwell, 1986, p. 78) .",
